Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.77,0:00:34.63,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,{What? }Sorry.{maybe just sorry and nuke the 'what'}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.93,0:00:36.49,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.68,0:00:40.56,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Whatever it was, it looks like you're fine now.{#}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.40,0:00:42.30,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.73,0:00:46.94,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,I'll take you home.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.80,0:00:49.65,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Thanks. I appreciate it.
