Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.94,0:03:18.92,Glasslip-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Hey, Yukinari.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.59,0:03:21.52,Glasslip-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Is our star finally making his return?{#}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.52,0:03:22.95,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,Glad to be back.{I've been looking forward to this.}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.95,0:03:24.86,Glasslip-Main,Guy2,0,0,0,,It's been a while. How're you feeling?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.86,0:03:27.27,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,Just seeing how things go, y'know?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.27,0:03:28.58,Glasslip-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Take it slow, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.58,0:03:29.35,Glasslip-Main,Coach,0,0,0,,Gather around!{#}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.44,0:03:44.82,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,{\i1}No...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.82,0:03:45.70,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,{\i1}No!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.18,0:03:47.23,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,{\i1}You listening?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.23,0:03:48.75,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,{\i1}The beach trip's off.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.20,0:04:28.03,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Oh, looks like he's here.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.03,0:04:29.04,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.79,0:04:35.33,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Yanagi-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.33,0:04:37.21,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Nice to see you again, ma'am.{#}{how to do name suggestions}{could just go with ma'am}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.21,0:04:41.53,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,It took an extra day, but she'll be discharged tonight.{released? =S}{discharged?}{like "...she'll be discharged from here tonight."}{makes more sense,}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.53,0:04:43.80,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Looks like I came just in time, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.89,0:04:48.64,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Thank you, Yanagi-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.64,0:04:49.45,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.45,0:04:51.36,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,We're just going to the roof.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.36,0:04:53.36,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,We'll be back in around twenty minutes!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.47,0:05:02.77,Glasslip-Main,Momo,0,0,0,,Hiro told me about you.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.77,0:05:04.42,Glasslip-Main,Momo,0,0,0,,You're in here for checkups, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.42,0:05:04.95,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.59,0:05:08.52,Glasslip-Main,Momo,0,0,0,,I brought sake buns today!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.52,0:05:10.03,Glasslip-Main,Momo,0,0,0,,Give Hiro my regards, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.37,0:05:14.33,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.56,0:05:23.97,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,You've been spending a lot\Nof time with Hiro lately, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.51,0:05:25.61,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.61,0:05:27.85,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,It was written all over his face, y'see.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.44,0:05:32.37,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Did something happen\Nbetween the two of you?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.06,0:05:33.85,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.93,0:05:35.95,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,All right. I won't pry.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.96,0:05:42.88,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,I know the beach trip was canceled at the last minute because your hospital stay was extended,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.88,0:05:47.70,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,but I was looking forward to it, so I grabbed my swimsuit and went down anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.35,0:05:52.46,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,Oh. So you went with Yukinari-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.46,0:05:53.78,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Well, that's the thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.78,0:05:57.53,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,He packed and left for the track and field club's summer training camp.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.53,0:05:58.72,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Now, of all times.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.72,0:05:59.68,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.19,0:06:03.66,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Yeah. He didn't tell me about it either.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.48,0:06:06.05,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,Well, I won't ask.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.46,0:06:12.49,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,The reason I came here today was because I wanted to ask you something.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.50,0:06:14.84,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,And to check up on you, of course.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.27,0:06:21.45,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,I was just thinking there was something weird between Touko and David.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.27,0:06:26.72,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,I don't know when it happened, but it looks like they're together now. Did you know?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.50,0:06:29.49,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.05,0:06:33.83,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,It's like they're keeping a lot of things to themselves.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.83,0:06:35.95,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you knew anything about it.{#}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.18,0:06:38.20,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,If so, could you tell me?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.10,0:06:41.21,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Unless Touko asked you not to, of course.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.14,0:06:43.62,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,She didn't ask me, no.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.35,0:06:47.72,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,But I don't know much about it either.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.36,0:06:55.83,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,That boyfriend of yours didn't come today.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.83,0:06:56.70,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.53,0:07:00.94,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,I feel like having some cookies.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.94,0:07:03.25,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,I'll make you some tea.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.25,0:07:06.21,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,I hope you won't mind if I join you.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.21,0:07:06.88,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.19,0:07:19.24,Glasslip-Main,Toukomom,0,0,0,,Touko, are you awake?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.92,0:07:21.46,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Yeah, I am!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.74,0:07:30.93,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,Mom asked me to bring you this.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.39,0:07:33.53,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.57,0:07:36.33,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,Do you mind if I stay here for a bit?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.33,0:07:37.20,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.50,0:08:00.54,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.48,0:08:08.37,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,How is she?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.12,0:08:15.35,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Are you feeling better?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.35,0:08:16.12,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.83,0:08:19.22,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,What was that back then?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.22,0:08:22.29,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Sorry. I'm not so sure myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.02,0:08:25.31,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Do you want to meet?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.39,0:08:28.45,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Aren't you afraid you'll see\Nsomething like that again?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.90,0:08:31.44,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Where do you want to meet?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.44,0:08:32.63,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.63,0:08:35.49,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I want to go see Jonathan.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.49,0:08:37.79,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,All right. Sounds good.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.79,0:08:39.19,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,See you in an hour, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.19,0:08:39.89,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.61,0:08:50.32,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Touko said that your checkups would go just fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.32,0:08:53.10,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,It was almost as if she knew\Nwhat would happen in the future.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.10,0:08:54.01,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.01,0:08:57.84,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Now that I think of it, when David first came to Kazemichi,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.84,0:09:00.23,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,he said something about seeing\Nthe same thing as her, didn't he?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.07,0:09:04.12,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,"I saw the same thing {as }you did," wasn't it?{check for quote}{full quote is "I saw the same thing you did that day."}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.81,0:09:06.23,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,You know something, don't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.46,0:09:10.58,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,Like I said earlier, I don't know much.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.22,0:09:15.54,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,I guess it'd be easier if I just\Ntold you everything I do know.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.85,0:09:21.54,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,I think Touko-chan and David have a special relationship.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.19,0:09:25.12,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Sachi,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.71,0:09:27.23,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,could it be that you...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.13,0:09:33.16,Glasslip-Main,Coach,0,0,0,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.16,0:09:34.30,Glasslip-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.63,0:09:36.14,Glasslip-Main,Guy2,0,0,0,,The other day...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.14,0:09:36.67,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.26,0:09:39.55,Glasslip-Main,Guy2,0,0,0,,At the track meet. Sorry for what I said.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.44,0:09:42.61,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,It's okay. I'm sorry too.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.21,0:09:47.44,Glasslip-Main,Coach,0,0,0,,Imi!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.44,0:09:48.58,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,Coach!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.18,0:10:04.54,Glasslip-Main,Momo,0,0,0,,I ran into Yana-chan at the hospital earlier.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.29,0:10:05.96,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.96,0:10:08.79,Glasslip-Main,Momo,0,0,0,,Huh? You're not going today?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.79,0:10:09.55,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.26,0:10:15.33,Glasslip-Main,Momo,0,0,0,,I bothered to put in a good word for you with that fragile glasses-girl of yours, you know?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.33,0:10:17.89,Glasslip-Main,Momo,0,0,0,,What's the point if you're not gonna make an effort yourself?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.89,0:10:18.47,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.22,0:10:24.64,Glasslip-Main,Momo,0,0,0,,So something {\i1}did{\i0} happen.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.38,0:10:35.27,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Kakeru, are you enjoying your life here?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.27,0:10:38.15,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Yeah, I am. I guess.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.09,0:10:39.77,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.95,0:10:52.67,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I'm going to school, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.67,0:10:54.08,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,Oh, Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.72,0:10:55.59,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.06,0:10:58.44,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry about earlier.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.44,0:10:59.49,Glasslip-Main,HIna,0,0,0,,No, it's not that.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.49,0:11:00.22,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.62,0:11:03.35,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,Um, it's about Yukinari-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.75,0:11:04.35,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.99,0:11:09.48,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not usually the type of person to do this, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.86,0:11:21.45,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.45,0:11:25.33,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,So, it was really unlike me\Nto get worked up like that,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.33,0:11:29.27,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,but I ended up chasing him down on my bike and telling him not to stop being cool.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.27,0:11:31.17,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,What? You talked to him?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.05,0:11:32.97,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.97,0:11:34.11,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.94,0:11:36.07,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.07,0:11:37.84,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,But what?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.25,0:11:40.82,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,I don't think he was out jogging yesterday.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.82,0:11:44.26,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,All the girls were telling me how much they'd been looking forward to seeing him.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.67,0:11:46.04,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.04,0:11:49.31,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,I have practice later today too, so I'll see what happens.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.27,0:11:51.24,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.88,0:11:53.21,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,He's not running.
Comment: 10,0:12:40.19,0:12:43.70,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,eyecatch
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.38,0:14:10.87,Glasslip-Main,Lady,0,0,0,,Shall we see it next time?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.87,0:14:11.90,Glasslip-Main,Lady2,0,0,0,,The crafting process?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.90,0:14:12.47,Glasslip-Main,Lady,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.47,0:14:12.97,Glasslip-Main,Lady2,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.77,0:14:22.29,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.32,0:14:26.55,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.00,0:15:01.99,Glasslip-Main,Girl,0,0,0,,Is he here?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.04,0:15:03.96,Glasslip-Main,Girl2,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.64,0:15:32.24,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Do you think we'll have to keep our distance\Nfrom each other from now on?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.73,0:15:34.24,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,No, I'm sure we won't.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.99,0:15:46.12,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I wonder what that was.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.26,0:15:50.66,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I'm a little scared to be around you.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.36,0:15:52.43,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,It sounds mean, I know.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.57,0:15:55.70,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I don't know what that was either.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.40,0:16:00.43,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,But I'm a little hesitant to come close to you, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.36,0:16:10.28,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.17,0:16:15.07,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry. It's from my sister.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.07,0:16:17.34,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,She said that Yuki-kun turned into Yana-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.25,0:16:25.58,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,The other day, Hina-chan—
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.17,0:16:28.21,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Oh, that's my little sister.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.91,0:16:32.18,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Hina-chan told me that Yuki-kun is their swimming club's—
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.18,0:16:35.14,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Oh, you don't mind me talking about Yuki-kun, do you?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.73,0:16:37.30,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Her swimming club's what?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.89,0:16:40.06,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Right. He's her swimming club's idol!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.78,0:16:48.63,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I tried calling Yana-chan, but she didn't pick up.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.63,0:16:52.19,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,From what you told me,\NTakayama didn't seem to be in a hurry.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.19,0:16:53.96,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I don't think there's much cause for concern.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.96,0:16:55.42,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,You think?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.42,0:16:56.98,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I hope so.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.24,0:17:02.58,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Kakeru-kun, are you worried about me?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.90,0:17:03.56,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.17,0:17:07.70,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I don't think you need to worry about Imi Yukinari,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.32,0:17:12.08,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,but if it bothers you that much,\NI'd be happy to take you to his house later.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.80,0:17:13.49,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.94,0:17:25.97,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,The other day, I was sketching here\Njust like this when I ran into Yuki-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.72,0:17:30.33,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Then we went to the art storeroom together for some pastels,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.96,0:17:37.36,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,and in that storeroom...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.99,0:17:42.40,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,{\i1}Touko, do you have a thing for that Kakeru guy?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.17,0:17:44.50,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.35,0:17:46.75,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you love him?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.42,0:17:50.38,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right. I see how it is.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.97,0:17:52.63,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, that's not—
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.13,0:17:56.38,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I was really shocked!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.38,0:18:00.05,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry. I'm going on about Yuki-kun again.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.71,0:18:03.25,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I see. So that's what happened.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.25,0:18:07.30,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,That's all that happened, though!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.25,0:18:12.71,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,But you were taken aback by it, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.71,0:18:13.44,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.31,0:18:16.39,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,If we go to that storeroom again,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.39,0:18:19.81,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,we may be able to learn something new about these fragments of the future.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.38,0:18:21.24,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.87,0:18:23.96,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Why don't we go together?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.13,0:18:27.14,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.14,0:18:27.80,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.66,0:18:30.56,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.56,0:18:31.42,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,We might...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.42,0:18:32.42,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Which way?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.43,0:18:34.93,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Turn right at the foyer!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.16,0:18:42.01,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.52,0:18:55.65,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,It's here.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.14,0:19:26.55,Glasslip-Main,Phone,0,0,0,,The number you have dialed is currently out of range—
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.73,0:19:31.32,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I think it would be a good idea\Nto talk to Imi Yukinari or Takayama.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.31,0:19:33.15,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.90,0:19:35.88,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Why do you think we should tell everyone?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.59,0:19:41.08,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,How do you think Takayama felt\Nwhen she saw us at the beach that day?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.08,0:19:42.69,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,"How"?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.69,0:19:44.63,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sure she was surprised.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.63,0:19:46.19,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Just surprised, you think?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.19,0:19:46.62,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.48,0:19:51.12,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Takayama will most likely\Nask you what happened.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.65,0:19:53.56,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,But how am I supposed to explain it to her?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.22,0:19:55.84,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I doubt she'll believe any of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.25,0:20:00.34,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,If anything like that happens again...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.68,0:20:03.93,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,What? Do you think it will?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.45,0:20:05.30,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.79,0:20:09.59,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.38,0:20:29.95,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Kakeru-kun, this is...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.20,0:20:49.28,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Huh? Was that...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.28,0:20:50.81,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,a fragment of the future?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.60,0:20:55.60,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Hey, what happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.82,0:21:04.09,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.09,0:21:06.07,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Touko! What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.07,0:21:07.41,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,What did you see?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.10,0:21:16.44,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.41,0:21:17.83,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Touko!
