Dialogue: 10,0:23:30.84,0:23:32.03,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Let's go to that storeroom again.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:32.03,0:23:33.74,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,I'm going to make myself anew!
