Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.71,0:22:08.68,ED-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}Take a deep breath and shape this world
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.68,0:22:14.39,ED-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}and bring me back to life again.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.19,0:22:26.66,ED-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}Hearts are fragile like glass
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.36,0:22:31.54,ED-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}and shatter into pieces when they're broken.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:32.58,0:22:38.00,ED-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}I gingerly wrapped those of mine and sent them to you.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:38.00,0:22:42.67,ED-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}Let me know which shard you've kept close.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.00,0:22:47.68,ED-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}Memories of our days together calmly pass us by.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.34,0:22:53.31,ED-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}There's rarely ever a day we wouldn't look back on.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:53.68,0:22:58.48,ED-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}And before we knew it,
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.90,0:23:02.94,ED-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}all our moments together had long slipped into the past.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.94,0:23:09.91,ED-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}The scenery I caught but a glimpse of
Dialogue: 1,0:23:09.91,0:23:14.79,ED-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}when I peered through the looking glass
Dialogue: 1,0:23:14.79,0:23:23.38,ED-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}was of a world yet unknown to both you and me
Dialogue: 1,0:23:23.38,0:23:28.43,ED-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}that shined ever so brightly out of our reach.
